## The Transfer Object

| Parameter  | Value |
|:-----------|:------|
| `object` | *(string)* 'transfer' |
| `id` | *(string)* Transfer Id |
| `amount` | *(integer)* Transfer amount in the smallest currency unit (e.g. satang, cent, ... ) |
| `currency` | *(string)* The currency as its lower-cased international 3-letter code, defined by the [ISO 4217](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217) standard. |
| `created` | *(datetime, format: [iso8601](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601))* Creation date of the transfer |

